<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Jaisalmer — TripAdvisor</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Nunito:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f0e8;
      --surface: #ede8dd;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --ink: #2a2118;
      --muted: #7a6e60;
      --accent: #00AA6C;
      --accent2: #34E0A1;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
      --green-grad: linear-gradient(135deg, #00AA6C 0%, #34E0A1 100%);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; min-height: 100vh; }

    .navbar {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(245,240,232,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .navbar-inner {
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 6vw; height: 64px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-logo-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--accent2); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 17px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(52,224,161,0.35); }
    .nav-logo span { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .nav-logo span b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .greeting-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: rgba(52,224,161,0.12); border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.2); border-radius: 100px; padding: 5px 14px; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); }
    .avatar { width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--green-grad); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 900; font-size: 0.9rem; color: white; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,170,108,0.35); }
    .avatar:hover { transform: scale(1.08); }
    .btn-profile { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,170,108,0.35); border-radius: 10px; padding: 7px 16px; text-decoration: none; background: white; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .btn-profile:hover { background: rgba(0,170,108,0.07); }
    .btn-logout { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; padding: 6px 14px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.15); border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .btn-logout:hover { border-color: #e05252; color: #e05252; }
    .back-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .back-btn:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .back-btn svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

    .hero { position: relative; height: 88vh; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; }
    .hero-img { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; filter: brightness(0.55) saturate(0.9); }
    .hero-grad { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(42,33,24,0.95) 0%, rgba(42,33,24,0.2) 55%, transparent 100%); }
    .hero-content { position: relative; padding: 0 8vw 4rem; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.3s forwards; }
    .hero-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent2); font-weight: 700; background: rgba(52,224,161,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(52,224,161,0.3); border-radius: 100px; padding: 4px 14px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #f5f0e8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .hero-meta { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; }
    .meta-label { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5); font-weight: 600; }
    .meta-value { font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.9); font-weight: 500; }

    .content { padding: 5rem 8vw; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .intro { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; margin-bottom: 5rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .intro-lead { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink); font-style: italic; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    .intro-body p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-weight: 500; }

    .sec-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .sec-label { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; }
    .sec-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

    .photo-section { margin-bottom: 5rem; }
    .photo-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); grid-template-rows: 260px 260px 260px; gap: 8px; }
    .photo-grid .p1 { grid-column: 1 / 6; grid-row: 1; }
    .photo-grid .p2 { grid-column: 6 / 13; grid-row: 1; }
    .photo-grid .p3 { grid-column: 1 / 5; grid-row: 2; }
    .photo-grid .p4 { grid-column: 5 / 9; grid-row: 2; }
    .photo-grid .p5 { grid-column: 9 / 13; grid-row: 2; }
    .photo-grid .p6 { grid-column: 1 / 7; grid-row: 3; }
    .photo-grid .p7 { grid-column: 7 / 13; grid-row: 3; }

    .photo-item { overflow: hidden; border-radius: 8px; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .photo-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; transition: transform 0.5s ease, filter 0.5s ease; filter: brightness(0.9) saturate(0.95); }
    .photo-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); filter: brightness(1) saturate(1.1); }
    .photo-caption { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: white; font-weight: 600; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(42,33,24,0.75) 0%, transparent 100%); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
    .photo-item:hover .photo-caption { opacity: 1; }

    .highlights { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
    .highlight-item { background: var(--card); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem 1.8rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: all 0.25s; }
    .highlight-item:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,170,108,0.1); border-color: rgba(0,170,108,0.25); }
    .hi-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; background: var(--green-grad); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
    .hi-label { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .hi-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 500; }

    .tips-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .tip-item { background: var(--card); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); transition: all 0.25s; }
    .tip-item:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,170,108,0.08); }
    .tip-title { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .tip-text { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 500; }

    footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); padding: 2.5rem 8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 5rem; }
    .footer-brand { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); }
    .footer-brand b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

    @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .photo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: repeat(4, 200px); }
      .photo-grid .p1 { grid-column: 1 / 3; grid-row: 1; }
      .photo-grid .p2 { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 2; }
      .photo-grid .p3 { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 2; }
      .photo-grid .p4 { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 3; }
      .photo-grid .p5 { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 3; }
      .photo-grid .p6 { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 4; }
      .photo-grid .p7 { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 4; }
      .highlights { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .tips-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="navbar">
  <div class="navbar-inner">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;">
      <a href="/home" class="nav-logo">
        <div class="nav-logo-icon">🦉</div>
        <span>Trip<b>Advisor</b></span>
      </a>
      <span style="color:var(--border);font-size:1rem">|</span>
      <a href="/explore" class="back-btn">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M5 12l7-7M5 12l7 7"/></svg>
        Explore India
      </a>
      <span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.75rem">/ Jaisalmer</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
        <span class="greeting-pill">👋 Hey, <%= user.name.split(' ')[0] %>!</span>
        <a href="/profile" class="avatar" title="Profile"><%= user.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase() %></a>
        <a href="/profile" class="btn-profile">👤 Profile</a>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn-logout">Logout</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login" style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;">Sign In</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <img class="hero-img"
    src="https://imgs.search.brave.com/DTDjpboV6SfPjlWPe3L7YHngAM079XmwpTfmkXo8d_A/rs:fit:860:0:0:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu/cmFqYXN0aGFuZGly/ZWN0LmNvbS93cC1j/b250ZW50L3VwbG9h/ZHMvMjAxMi8xMS9K/YWlzYWxtZXItRm9y/dC5qcGc"
    alt="Jaisalmer Fort" />
  <div class="hero-grad"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-tag">🏜️ Rajasthan — India</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Jaisalmer</h1>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Also Known As</span><span class="meta-value">The Golden City</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Best Time to Visit</span><span class="meta-value">October — February</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Known For</span><span class="meta-value">Desert, Fort, Havelis, Dunes</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-label">Nearest Airport</span><span class="meta-value">Jaisalmer Airport</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<main class="content">
  <div class="intro">
    <p class="intro-lead">"Jaisalmer is not a city you arrive at — it is a city that rises out of the earth, golden and impossible, as if the desert itself conjured it."</p>
    <div class="intro-body">
      <p>Standing alone in the heart of the Thar Desert, Jaisalmer is one of Rajasthan's most extraordinary cities. Built almost entirely from golden-yellow Jurassic limestone, it glows amber at sunrise and deepens to burnt gold at sunset — earning it the name Sonar Qila, the Golden Fort.</p>
      <p>The centrepiece is Jaisalmer Fort, a 12th-century UNESCO World Heritage Site that remains one of the few "living forts" in the world — roughly 3,000 people still live, work, and worship within its walls. Narrow lanes wind past ornately carved havelis, Jain temples adorned with intricate stonework, and rooftop cafés looking out over the desert horizon.</p>
      <p>Beyond the city, the Sam Sand Dunes stretch endlessly into the Thar. At dawn and dusk, the dunes shift in colour from pale gold to deep ochre. Camel safaris, desert camps under the stars, and folk music around a fire at night make Jaisalmer a place that lingers long after you leave.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="photo-section">
    <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-label">Gallery</span><div class="sec-line"></div></div>
    <div class="photo-grid">
      <div class="photo-item p1">
        <img src="https://thecarvaanresort.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/jaisalmer-fort-in-rajasthan-1200x480.jpg" alt="Jaisalmer Fort" loading="lazy" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Jaisalmer Fort — Sonar Qila</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-item p2">
        <img src="https://www.bharatbooking.com/admin/webroot/img/uploads/holiday-package-gallery/1700201154_34594-sam-sand-dunes-jaisalmer-rajasthan-tour-slider-image.webp" alt="Sam Sand Dunes" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509316785289-025f5b846b35?w=800&q=80'" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Sam Sand Dunes</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-item p3">
        <img src="https://thecarvaanresort.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/patwon-ki-haveli-jaisalmer-rajasthan-1-attr-hero-1024x576.jpg" alt="Patwon Ki Haveli" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524492412937-b28074a5d7da?w=800&q=80'" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Patwon Ki Haveli</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-item p4">
        <img src="https://images.travelandleisureasia.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/03/24180138/jaisalmer-tourist-attractions-fi.jpeg?tr=w-1200,q-60" alt="Jaisalmer at sunset" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800&q=80'" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Golden Hour, Jaisalmer</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-item p5">
        <img src="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/historic-jaisalmer-fort-rajasthan-india-made-yellow-limestone-known-as-golden-fort-golden-fort-jaisalmer-rajasthan-176166581.jpg" alt="Fort Entrance" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524492412937-b28074a5d7da?w=800&q=80'" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Fort Gateway</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-item p6">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/12/Gadisar_Lake%2C_Jaisalamer.jpg" alt="Gadisar Lake" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509316785289-025f5b846b35?w=800&q=80'" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Gadisar Lake</span>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-item p7">
        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRvGCVy5y9r5XAB_JOBVB8kzjwoy_0Phbt7sg&s" alt="Jain Temple Jaisalmer" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519677100203-a0e668c92439?w=800&q=80'" />
        <span class="photo-caption">Jain Temple Inside the Fort</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec-head"><span class="sec-label">Highlights</span><div class="sec-line"></div></div>
  <div class="highlights">
    <div class="highlight-item">
      <div class="hi-num">860+</div>
      <div class="hi-label">Years Old</div>
      <div class="hi-desc">Jaisalmer Fort was founded in 1156 AD by Rawal Jaisal of the Bhati Rajput clan. It has withstood sieges, invasions, and centuries of desert sun — and still stands proud.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight-item">
      <div class="hi-num">99</div>
      <div class="hi-label">Bastions in the Fort</div>
      <div class="hi-desc">The massive triangular fort walls are punctuated by 99 bastions, of which 92 are original 12th-century construction. It is among the world's largest fully intact medieval forts.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight-item">
      <div class="hi-num">3000</div>
      <div class="hi-label">Residents Inside the Fort</div>
      <div class="hi-desc">Unlike most forts that are now museums, Jaisalmer is a living fort — families, shops, guesthouses and temples all function within its ancient sandstone walls every single day.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sec-head" style="margin-top:5rem"><span class="sec-label">Travel Tips</span><div class="sec-line"></div></div>
  <div class="tips-grid">
    <div class="tip-item">
      <p class="tip-title">Best Time to Visit</p>
      <p class="tip-text">October to February is ideal — temperatures are mild and the Desert Festival (February) brings folk music, camel races, and turban-tying competitions to the dunes. Avoid summers where temperatures exceed 45°C.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-item">
      <p class="tip-title">Getting Around</p>
      <p class="tip-text">The fort and old city are best explored on foot. For the Sam Sand Dunes (42 km away), hire a shared jeep or auto. Overnight desert camps offer a full experience with camel safaris, dinner, and sleeping under the stars.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-item">
      <p class="tip-title">Don't Miss</p>
      <p class="tip-text">Sunrise on the Sam Dunes, the intricate carvings of Patwon Ki Haveli, the sunset view from the fort ramparts, and a rooftop dinner in the old city with the fort lit up in the background.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-item">
      <p class="tip-title">Where to Stay</p>
      <p class="tip-text">Staying inside the fort itself is atmospheric but heritage conservation efforts ask tourists to choose guesthouses outside the fort where possible, to reduce water and structural stress on the ancient walls.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <span class="footer-brand">Explore <b>India</b></span>
  <a href="/explore" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;">← Back to All Destinations</a>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
